    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >创建房间</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创建房间。设置自己的办公室。随心所欲地扩展办公室。从小型办公室转变为大型公司。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202250/extras/40515ac5c55ea3652ae1f3811df54ce8.poster.avif?t=1772014593\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202250/extras/40515ac5c55ea3652ae1f3811df54ce8.webm?t=1772014593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202250/extras/40515ac5c55ea3652ae1f3811df54ce8.mp4?t=1772014593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >办公室定制</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以选择布置您的办公空间。从各种家具中进行选择，让您的团队舒适高效。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202250/extras/4701134473df0f91f2e4bee0257d233f.poster.avif?t=1772014593\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202250/extras/4701134473df0f91f2e4bee0257d233f.webm?t=1772014593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202250/extras/4701134473df0f91f2e4bee0257d233f.mp4?t=1772014593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >招聘</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >聘请人才。您需要为每个部门配备员工。您需要保持办公室的平衡。您需要让您雇用的人的幸福感保持在高水平。您不想让有才华的员工流失到其他公司。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202250/extras/ebf3bfadd4246894f6a9a83489571a79.poster.avif?t=1772014593\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202250/extras/ebf3bfadd4246894f6a9a83489571a79.webm?t=1772014593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202250/extras/ebf3bfadd4246894f6a9a83489571a79.mp4?t=1772014593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >制作游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作自己的游戏项目。增加您的关注者。撼动排行榜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202250/extras/d372ad808cbf7e47badcb62894537685.poster.avif?t=1772014593\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202250/extras/d372ad808cbf7e47badcb62894537685.webm?t=1772014593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202250/extras/d372ad808cbf7e47badcb62894537685.mp4?t=1772014593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >员工跟踪</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用相机跟踪那些试图逃避工作的人，并让他们重返工作岗位。因为您将有一个特定的时间表来完成工作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202250/extras/cf9978d3b9998b8089d72c1466e96dd0.poster.avif?t=1772014593\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202250/extras/cf9978d3b9998b8089d72c1466e96dd0.webm?t=1772014593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202250/extras/cf9978d3b9998b8089d72c1466e96dd0.mp4?t=1772014593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
